Investec Says U.K. Unit’s Full-Year Profit to Rise, South Africa’s in Line

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-17T08:54:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/investec-says-u-k-unit-s-full-year-profit-to-rise-south-africa-s-in-line.html
Investec Ltd. said its U.K.
business is expected to post an operating profit ahead of the
previous year while its South African operation is expected to
post an operating profit in line with the earlier 12-month
period.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
